 balance between result accuracy (precision) and missed barcodes (recall) for linear barcodes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Some barcode types are naturally prone to false positives (e.g. MSI Plessey)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For those barcode types false positives can be drastically reduced (precision can be increased) by requiring that multiple scan-lines in the input scan to the same result."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, this stronger condition can lead to missed barcodes (lower recall)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Confirmation is avoided for barcode types, which are by design resistant to false positives, (e.g. Code128) to maximize recall."}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkonedconfirmationmode"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK/SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode/init(rawValue:)":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode\/init(rawValue:)","role":"symbol","title":"init(rawValue:)","fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"?(","kind":"text"},{"text":"rawValue","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkonedconfirmationmode\/init(rawvalue:)"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK":{"title":"ScanbotSDK","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Version: 8.0.3"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk"}},"variantOverrides":[{"patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotSDK~1SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode\/title","value":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode"},{"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotS